inlinehook 计算出 x8 的地址

```
function inline_hook() {
    var libnative_lib_addr = Module.findBaseAddress("libmatch06.so");
        var _0x04d140 = libnative_lib_addr.add(0x4A674);//x8 动态跳转函数
        Java.perform(function () {
            Interceptor.attach(_0x04d140, {
                onEnter: function (args) {
                console.log("x8",(parseInt(this.context.x8)-libnative_lib_addr).toString(16))//得到加密函数，
                },
                onLeave: function (retval) {
                }
            })
        })
}

```

```
function sub_49E68() {
var str_name_func =0x49E68;
    var base_addr = Module.findBaseAddress("libmatch06.so");
    var pointer = base_addr.add(str_name_func)
    Interceptor.attach(pointer,
        {
            onEnter: function (args) {
                myhexdump("0x4b450 arg0",args[0],64)//结果
               console.log('0x61D18 arg1:' + parseInt(args[1]));
               myhexdump('0x4b450 arg2:', args[1], parseInt(args[2]))
                console.log('0x4b450 arg2:'+parseInt(args[2]));
                this.buffer=args[3]
                            },
            onLeave: function (retval) {
                myhexdump('0x4b450 ret:',  this.buffer, 32)
            }
        }
    );
}

```
```
    public String call_49E68() {
        List<Object> list = new ArrayList<>(10);
        String arg1="C5A6D4F9B38E0721";
        String arg2="1652624068909$E6:CA:E3:4D:6A:08";
        int arg3 = arg2.getBytes().length;
        MemoryBlock memoryBlock1 = emulator.getMemory().malloc(arg1.getBytes().length, false);
        // get memory pointer
        UnidbgPointer input_ptr1 = memoryBlock1.getPointer();
        // write plainText on it
        input_ptr1.write(arg1.getBytes());
        MemoryBlock memoryBlock2 = emulator.getMemory().malloc(arg3, false);
        // get memory pointer
        UnidbgPointer input_ptr2 = memoryBlock2.getPointer();
        // write plainText on it
        input_ptr2.write(arg2.getBytes());
        // arg3 -- buffer
        MemoryBlock memoryBlock3 = emulator.getMemory().malloc(32, false);
        UnidbgPointer output_buffer=memoryBlock3.getPointer();
        list.add(input_ptr1);
        list.add(input_ptr2);
        list.add(arg3);
        list.add(output_buffer);
        module.callFunction(emulator, 0x49E68, list.toArray());
        System.out.println("结果存放地址："+output_buffer);
        Inspector.inspect(output_buffer.getByteArray(0, 32), "output");
        return byte2HexString(output_buffer.getByteArray(0, 32));
    }
```

W8, [X21,X24]：从 x21 加载数据，赋值 w8

W9, [X9,X26]：从 x9 加载数据，赋值给 w9

MOV  W10, #8：8 赋值给 w10

EOR  W8, W9, W8：w9 和 w8 进行异或操作，结果赋值到 w8
